des:
Whether it's managing a team at work, allotting tasks to family members, or just categorizing your different to-do lists, GTM (Group Tasks Manager) is your simple sidekick for staying organized. 

With GTM you can : 
1. Add or Delete unique team/family members.
2. Create personalized lists for everyone. 
3. Remove tasks once complete.
4. Reset all lists once finished with a project. 

GTM is free to use forever and will have no promotional content ever.

SAMPLE UTTERANCES :

AddPerson: 
add {Person}
create {Person}
setup {Person}

AddTask: 
tell {Person} to {Task}
remind {Person} to {Task}
ask {Person} to {Task}
add {Task} for {Person}

ListTasks: 
what are the tasks for {Person}
what are the items for {Person}
what are {Person} tasks
what are {Person} items
list tasks for {Person}
list items for {Person}

RemoveTask:
remove task {Number} for {Person}
remove item {Number} for {Person}
delete task {Number} for {Person}
delete item {Number} for {Person}
remove {Person} task {Number}
remove {Person} item {Number}
delete {Person} task {Number}
delete {Person} item {Number}

ClearTasks 
clear tasks for {Person}
clear items for {Person}
delete tasks for {Person}
delete items for {Person}
delete {Person} tasks
delete {Person} items
clear {Person} items

ResetList:
clear
reset
start over
